videos.description: Tomas Woldetensae misses the long 3-pointer and Jay Huff grabs the rebound and finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Virginia's Huff stuffs in the dunk

videos.description: Elijah Hughes sees that no defenders are guarding him, so he takes off and slams it home with authority.
